        'privacy.title': 'Privacy Policy',
        'privacy.updated': 'Last updated: March 10, 2026',
        'privacy.intro.title': 'Overview',
        'privacy.intro.desc': 'Youran Tab (hereinafter referred to as "this extension") is an open-source browser new tab extension. We highly value your privacy. This extension does not collect, store, or transmit any personal user data.',
        'privacy.collect.title': 'Data Collection',
        'privacy.collect.desc': 'This extension does not collect any personal information or usage data. All configuration data (including site lists, theme settings, background settings, etc.) is stored in the browser\'s local storage and is never sent to any external server. When you use Add from Current Tabs, the extension only reads the titles and URLs of the tabs currently open in the active browser window locally, so it can show the selection list and create sites faster.',
        'privacy.storage.title': 'Local Storage',
        'privacy.storage.desc': 'This extension uses the browser\'s local storage (localStorage / chrome.storage.local) to save your personalized settings. This data is stored entirely on your device. You can back up your data at any time using the extension\'s export feature, or clear all data by uninstalling the extension.',
        'privacy.network.title': 'Network Requests',
        'privacy.network.desc': 'This extension only makes network requests when fetching site icons, retrieving favicons from public icon services. Other than that, this extension does not send requests to any server.',
