        'privacy.permissions.title': 'Permissions',
        'privacy.permissions.desc': 'This extension only requests the minimum permissions required to operate. The added tabs permission is used only to read the titles and URLs of tabs currently open in the active browser window. It does not read, and cannot read, page content, form input, personal identity data, account information, passwords, or payment data. It also does not access your browsing history or bookmarks.',
        'privacy.changes.title': 'Policy Changes',
